Portland is full of people who love many things. We have people who chase our dreams, or think about chasing our dreams while we drink too much at the bar. Portland has problems. We have a drug problem. It usually comes from mental health problems. The rain and clouds can make people feel sad. We also have a homelessness problem. Many people come here because we have good services. But our services are not enough. People who have homes are sometimes kind, sometimes angry. This is the same in other parts of the country. We are not weird in feeling this way.

There are mountains in the north. They watch the sun every day. They see the sun come up and go down. They are always there. I forget about them sometimes. Work and life take my attention. But they are still there. They are strong and steady. They do not change. When I am very stressed, I think about them. They remind me to take a deep breath and to be strong. I moved here when I started college. The mountains near my school were beautiful. I loved them at first. The school has nice buildings and a pond. But the mountains are special to me. The town is nice too. There are many coffee shops where I studied. I can walk or take a bus to the downtown area. It is old and interesting. There are old buildings and restaurants. It is busy and exciting. But it is not busy for long. I can go back to a quiet part of town. The library is there. It is a place to rest. I like this town because it is different in different parts. It is a nice place to live. I have good memories here. I walked with friends in the park. We went to the movies in a nice theater. But I also have sad memories. We all have sad memories. The ponds are a good place to think and cry. I went to the pond at night and wondered about my life. I looked at the animals and thought about my purpose. I walked to the main street and saw the sun. The sun was shining and made the sky beautiful. I looked at the mountains and I felt strong. They reminded me to be strong and to keep going.

If you plan to visit Bensonhurst in Brooklyn, you will have no trouble finding it. The city has good public transportation. Bensonhurst is a busy neighborhood like the rest of New York City. You will see many Asian stores as you walk. Many Asian people live in Bensonhurst. This is why you will find an Asian store on almost every block. Supermarkets and laundromats are popular. People like these stores because food is good, prices are low, and they are easy to use.

Near my home, there are four Asian supermarkets within a short walk. This is helpful for buying groceries. Bensonhurst is a mixed area. Many immigrants and their children live here. Some big businesses in the area are owned by Asian people. There is also a park nearby. The park has many basketball courts, a big field for soccer or baseball, handball courts, a playground for children, and a water fountain for kids to play in during the summer.

The area has many small homes and co-op buildings. Few big buildings are here. Many people are friendly, but some can be noisy. Cars often play music loudly as they drive by. You may hear a car starting quickly in the morning. At night, be careful. Some people can be mean. You may meet people who want to cause trouble. I was once bullied here. But that was a long time ago. Recently, someone took a package from my home. This is a common problem in Bensonhurst. People do not clean up after their dogs. Every day, you will see dog waste on the street. This is my biggest problem.

I live in a place with few sidewalks. People have to walk on the road because there are no sidewalks. The road can be a little bit bad to drive on because it has holes in some places. There are many telephone and electric wires above the road. They look bad because they get broken in storms and need to be fixed many times.

My house is at the top of the biggest hill in the neighborhood. People call it the "work-out hill" because many runners like to run up the hill. The houses are built high up so people can see the ocean.

There are many tall trees around my house. People do not like the trees because they block the view of the ocean. But the trees are nice when the sun sets. The water looks nice and the sky turns orange.

It often rains and storms in our area. Moss grows on everything, including houses, cars and railings. One time I left my car outside for a month and it got covered in moss. It took me three hours to clean it off.

There are not many children in my neighborhood. The people are mostly older and many are retired. They have dogs instead of children. The dogs are always running around and sometimes they get into people's houses.

We have many wild rabbits. They dig up gardens and burrow into lawns. My cats like to catch them and there are not many rabbits left in our neighborhood.

We see many birds, like small birds and hummingbirds. Sometimes a hawk or eagle comes by, but the crows chase it away.

There are no stores in my neighborhood. But if you walk down to the waterfront, you can find some restaurants that serve fresh seafood. The beach is not very big, but it is fun to throw rocks into the water.

I live in a small town in Tennessee. My house is on a street between two main roads. This means we have some traffic, but it is a quiet neighborhood. People do not move in and out often. I know most of my neighbors. They work in their yards and do other daily things. In the winter, we sled down a small hill. We live at the corner of the street. We see all the people who come and go. We take note of strangers' cars. Some neighbors walk for exercise or to walk their dogs. Children ride their bikes. We work from home. There are four of us: my wife, our two daughters, and me. We are at home a lot. We go outside and play, even in the rain. We sometimes grill on our back deck. It smells good. We hear lawn mowers almost every day from March to October. It is a wooded area, so we have trees and shade. We rake and burn leaves in the fall. I like the smell of burning leaves. It means fall is here. We do not have much winter. It feels like a long fall. My garage is at the back of the house. I like to work on my truck in the garage. When the doors are open, I feel close to my neighbors. On holidays, it is quiet. We have visitors on Thanksgiving and other holidays like Mother's day and Christmas. I like living here. If the street were not a main road, it would be perfect.

I live in a neighborhood in the middle of a dry and sandy area. This area is very different from many other places. When you look around, you see mostly brown and dirt. It is not very green like some other places. Sometimes I see a small green area, like a lawn. But this is very expensive to take care of. When I first moved here, there were many houses far apart. Now there are more houses, and it looks like a small city.

People in my neighborhood are generally friendly. But, like any place, it has good and bad parts. Many old people live in my neighborhood, and it is a nice place. There are some stores, but not many. Most of the stores are part of big chains, like Food 4 Less and Smart & Final. If you want to buy healthy food, you have to go somewhere else. My city is not very developed, and there are many open spaces. This is why many people work in construction. I work in construction, too. I install drywall and T-bars for a living.

I like my neighborhood because of the animals. People come to our area to see the beauty of the desert. The desert has a special climate and geography that supports many different kinds of wildlife. People who live here should learn about the animals that live here so we can live together safely. My family loves animals, and we have learned a lot about them. We even try to catch them when we can. If you come to visit, there are some things to see. Victorville is a good place for families to learn about the desert. You can visit the San Bernardino County Fair, which is a fun event. You can also visit Wrightwood to see the snow-covered mountains and learn winter sports. If you are interested in the natural history and culture of the desert, you can visit the Victor Valley Museum. It has many interesting things to see, like rocks, old bones, and Native American artifacts.

My neighborhood is the college campus where I live. I live in a dormitory with many people from different countries and ages. My neighborhood also includes the campus area around my dorm. I like my neighborhood. It has many things like homes, people, stores, and a park.

Let's talk about the homes in my neighborhood. There are three kinds of homes. Some are apartments, some are houses, and some are dorm rooms. Apartments have 2-4 people in each room. There are 4-6 rooms on each floor. Some buildings are 2 floors high. So, about 20 people live in each building. Some houses are for rent. They have 2-4 bedrooms. Only a few people live in these houses. Most students live in dorm rooms. Two people share a room, sometimes.

My college is proud of its diversity. People from many countries and ages live in my neighborhood. Some staff members live in houses. New students live in dorms and older students live in apartments. Let's talk about the stores and park. My school is a closed neighborhood. It has many stores and one park. The stores have food, clothes, and things we need. We can buy anything we need in our neighborhood. The park is a fun place for everyone. It is clean and safe because all neighbors take care of it.

I have lived in this neighborhood for 10 years. I am happy to share what I know about it. When I first came here, I was sad. I missed my friends and family from Riverdale. My mom and dad wanted the best for me and my sister, so we moved to Stockbridge. Our new neighborhood was better. It had good housing and a good high school. I made new friends and enemies in school. I did not get to know my neighbors very well, but I liked Mr. Glen and his children. They are kind people. I remember their wedding. My family and I attended. We had a good time. I even caught a white strap that Mrs. Glen took off her leg. I did not catch the flowers, though. I like to visit the park and walk in nature. It makes me feel calm. I also like to practice my balance with sticks. I have a wooden sword that I like to play with. There is a basketball and tennis court. I used to play tennis with my dad and Mr. Graves. We had fun, but we worked hard. I hope I can play again. I have had some happy times in this neighborhood. I think there is more to come.

I live near the college I attend. It is very convenient for me. Many apartment buildings are in my area. Some are old, but they have been renovated inside. There are also some restaurants and bars. They are fun to go to and not very expensive. One bar changed its name recently. It is a bit more expensive, but the service and drinks are good.

Most people in my area are students or have low incomes. They live in apartments because they are not very expensive. There is an elementary school near my home. Many children live in the area. My neighbors are not very friendly. They smoke a lot. I do not want to know them.

My apartment building is old, but it has a lot of trees around it. Some trees were cut down, but there are still many trees. The street behind my building has another set of apartments. The street next to mine is not as nice. The sidewalks are bad, and the buildings look old. There are many trees on that street to hide the bad buildings. Much crime happens on that street. But crime happens in other places too.

I like where I live. I can afford it. There are many good things near my home. The college is close, and I can easily ride a bus to go shopping or downtown.

My neighborhood has duplex homes on a circle street. They look like individual houses. Each one is painted yellow with white porches and green metal roofs. Almost everyone is friends with each other. We stand at the end of our driveways sometimes and talk while our children play outside. It is nice to be in a place without many cars and computers. It is like going back in time.

We are surrounded by fields, trees, and blue skies with white clouds. But we also have problems. This season, we have had tornado warnings. Last night, we heard the tornado sirens. We went to our shelter. I was in my bathtub with my small dog and a few things. My big dog stayed in the living room. It was quiet outside except for the sound of hail on the ground.

After the storm, the road was hot. We had a big change in temperature. The hail melted on the hot pavement. The sun came out and it started to rain. A double rainbow happened. I took pictures with my camera. My friends were impressed. The neighborhood stayed quiet for a little while. Then people came home from wherever they were.

We have a good community. We are close to the city of Charlotte. Every morning, we hear roosters crowing from the nearby farms. It is like living in a small village. We even have a donkey that brays in the evening. I am lucky to live here.

We have duplex homes on our street. Each one looks the same from the outside. But the inside is different. Some are small. I like to walk in the big field behind my house. I see deer and hear a bullfrog singing in the morning. It is a great place to live. We have a pond that is not for swimming. I like it here, 40 minutes from the city.

I moved to this neighborhood one year before I started eighth grade. It was hard to make friends at first, but I made two friends who lived near me. One lives two houses down, and the other lives on my street. They do not live there anymore, but I still have happy memories. The people who lived here when I first moved here are still here. My neighborhood is like many American neighborhoods. It has two-story houses and a park. I like this about my neighborhood.

Every weekend, I hear kids playing outside. The neighborhood is quiet most days. I have never had a problem with anyone in my neighborhood. They leave you alone unless you need help. I have ordered many packages online and they have never been stolen from my porch.

The park is near my house. I have happy memories there. I played basketball, football, and baseball with my friends. But I also got hurt playing football. The good memories are more important. When I go to the park now, I spend time with my little cousin's kids. They like playing on swings and slides. The park makes me feel happy and sad at the same time.

My neighborhood is diverse. You can find many kinds of food nearby. There are Chinese, Indian, Mexican, and Italian restaurants within a short distance. Many people use apps to get food delivered. There are also fast food shops and pizza places. The stores near my house have everything we need. There are dry cleaners, a pharmacy, and a grocery store. There are even stores that sell Indian food. I like my neighborhood.

When I read about problems with neighbors on social media, I feel happy to have the friends and neighborhood I have.

I live in a small town in South Carolina. It is not a big town, but it is important for farming. Johnston is known as the Peach Capital of the World. This is what the welcome sign says. The town is mostly farmland with many peach trees and cattle. The houses are far apart and two stories high. They have metal or gray roofs to keep out the hot sun. Most houses are not near the road. They are far back so people can use the front land for animals and crops.

In the main part of town, there is one traffic light. This is where you will find the town's stores. There are three places to get fast food. One is Hong Kong, a small Chinese restaurant. Another is Fiesta Mexican Restaurant. The third is Gary's, a small burger place. There used to be a pizzeria, but it is closed now.

There is a small pharmacy called Maxwell and Halford Drug. People like to buy Cherry Coca-Cola there. There is one grocery store called IGA. It is not very big, so people often go to a bigger store in another town. The most popular store is Dollar General. It sells many things and is very busy. There is a furniture store called Possibilities Furniture & More. They deliver the furniture you buy. Next to the store is a place to take care of your pet called Clark's Cuts and Kennels.

The doctor and the vet are in separate buildings outside the main part of town. They are small, but they can help the people of Johnston. There is one school called Johnston Elementary School. When students finish fifth grade, they go to school in the next town. We are making a new park with a playground and other fun things. But right now, there is not much to do in our town. We do not have a movie theater, bowling alley, or many restaurants. But it is a nice town. You can easily miss it if you are driving by!

I first heard about my town on a podcast. It was about people who were missing. I was surprised. Almost every apartment in my area is expensive. It costs over one thousand dollars a month. I had not heard about this story before. My friends did not know about it either. Maybe it is hard for people to hear. I know some of my friends cry at night. Life is expensive, but we have learned to save money. We like second-hand things. We like the smell of old toys and old clothes. When you grow up, you smell less. As an adult, you might smoke or you might just be used to things being this way. But the flea market is always there. The smell of old magazines on a piano is strong. It stays in the leather even after you wash it.

There are three second-hand stores near my home. If you start on one side, you can visit two charity stores, a library, and a store with old books. Downtown is busy. Cars and people fill the streets every morning, but you cannot hear it in the thrift stores. No matter how many people or cars go by, the stores are quiet. It is a nice place to spend the afternoon. Every year, more and more people come to downtown. It is a growing city. One of the biggest companies for online shopping and delivery is here. It is still getting bigger. It reminds me of New York. Everyone is busy with their own goals. No one asks you for help. You can be alone and people will leave you alone. It is different from the South. In the South, people care about each other. They ask questions. You can keep to yourself in this city and it will not matter. It is a lively place to be. There is music from the man who plays the piano next door and the two singers upstairs. There is always something going on. We have less of an apartment of strangers and more of a community of friends. We help each other when we need it. We celebrate birthdays and help each other when someone dies. I am lucky to live here. I like most of my neighbors. They treat me well. I try to clean up after myself and I leave food for them. They do the same for me. It is nice to see them and I think they like my company as much as I like theirs. I live in a big, modern city, but it is my neighbors who make me feel good about my life.

I live in a typical suburban area. My neighborhood is very nice. It looks very well taken care of. The houses are all single family homes. The homeowner's association helps keep everything nice. The front yards are all the same. They have small lawns, some small rocks, and short driveways. Some houses have two cars. As you drive around the neighborhood, you see new concrete roads. The roads are good. There are no potholes. Most houses are one story, but some are two stories. We don't have mailboxes in front of each house. Instead, there are many boxes at the end of the street. You need a key to get your mail. There are two big boxes for packages.

My house is at the edge of the city. It's a mix of country and suburbs. We have a lot of space. There are many pools that everyone can use. They are well kept and locked. There are paths where you can walk your dog or take a walk. You don't need to go to a park to get exercise. The neighborhood is big, so you can run around it and get exercise. Many people who live here are retired. It's a safe area and people look out for each other. We also have some young and middle-aged people. The city is big in population, but it has a small town feel. We have many things you need, like a mall. It's not very big, but it's enough. I can drive 15 minutes and find many stores. There are high-end stores with organic food and stores with low prices and few employees. My neighborhood is safe, clean, and nice. We have many good things, like pools and walking paths. If we need to go shopping, we can drive to a big store.

I live in a small town in the Midwest. It is near a big city. My neighborhood is on the east side of the town. Many people who live here have low incomes. The houses are not expensive. My neighbors are friendly. They say hello when I walk down the street. There is some crime in the area. A few people have been hurt in shootings. Our next-door neighbors' son was killed in a shooting last year. We have not been hurt by crime. Sometimes we lose small things from our porch.

The town is having problems with a sickness from a drug called fentanyl. Many people have died from it. But there are places to help people with addiction. My son goes to a good school. He has extra help because he needs it. He has friends and teachers who care about him. He loves his school. The school gives free food to all students. No one is treated differently because they do not have enough money.

The town is improving. They have fixed some roads and parks. But most of the changes are on the west side of town. My neighborhood is not as nice as some other parts of town. We like living here. People are friendly, the schools are good, and there are many stores to buy things. Our home is not worth a lot of money, but it is comfortable.

We have lived here for over 16 years. We do not want to live anywhere else.

My neighborhood is full of culture. It is on a hill. Many old buildings are there. I live in a seven-story apartment building near an old theater. Across the street is a fun bar that people like to visit on warm summer nights. People wait in line to get in on weekends during June and July.

Nearby is a big park. It is nice for the area. The park has concrete around it and wide stairs. During cold winter months, homeless people set up tents. It is warmer for them to be close together.

I like my city's culture. It is not just about old buildings. The people are special. My neighborhood used to be bad because of gang violence. But the people work hard to keep it clean. They care about their city.

Some people say if you are white, do not walk around at night. I think this is a reminder of the past. I am not white. I think the people like me because I understand their problems. They are kind to me. They help me.

I feel good walking at night. People are nice. A laundromat owner let me charge my phone when I had no place to go. Someone gave me money and told me I am beautiful. The people here are special. I feel alive here.

I live in a small town in Michigan. It is a peaceful place. The town is near two big lakes, Lake Michigan and Lake Charlevoix. I like living here. It is a safe place. I can walk to many places. There is a park not far from my house. My neighborhood is quiet. Houses are not close together. They are old homes that have been updated. Many houses have yards with trampolines and playsets. People take care of their lawns. The grass is cut and the plants are trimmed.

It is a good place to raise a family. You can see children playing outside. People know each other in this town. They say hello when they see each other. The town has a sheriff's department and a health department. There is a recycling center where people take their trash. We also have baseball and softball fields. You can hear the announcers calling the games. There is a small airport near my house. I can hear the planes taking off and landing.

I like my neighborhood. It is not perfect, but it is a good place to live. It is safe and peaceful. My kids can ride their bikes to the park. It is only a few blocks away. I can walk to get ice cream from a local shop. It is a great place to live.
